# ── .lycheeignore ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Links that lychee should skip when checking for broken links.
# Supports regex patterns.
#
# Syntax:
#   https://example.com/skip-this-link
#   https://*.example.com/*    (regex supported)

# ── Local files that don't exist yet ──────────────────────────
# These are referenced in docs but are placeholders/future files
https://github.com/yourusername/opencs
https://github.com/yourusername/opencs/issues
file:///home

# ── Social / Authentication pages (often blocked by crawlers) ─
# BotFather and Telegram links may rate-limit crawlers
https://t.me/
# WhatsApp links
https://wa.me/

# ── Platform links that block automated checks ────────────────
https://platform.openai.com
https://ai.google.dev
https://anthropic.com
https://www.anthropic.com
